value.name: Murderer 🕹️ Play Murderer on CrazyGames
value.snippet: Murderer is a first-person detective multiplayer game that is inspired by games like Among Us and Werewolf. There are three roles, murderer, gunner, and civilian. The murderer has a knife and must kill all civilians, the gunner has a revolver and must kill the murderer, and civilians can find three clues and get a revolver. Release Date.

value.name: 7 of History's Most Notorious Serial Killers | Britannica
value.snippet: One of the world’s most prolific serial killers might still be out there. Pedro Lopez is linked to more than 300 murders in his native Colombia and in Ecuador and Peru. At least one-third of those murders were tribal women. After Lopez’s arrest in 1980, police found the graves of more than 50 of his preteen victims.
